Introduction
============
Lighttasks is a simple and lightweight task timer. It lets you keep track of how long you spend on certain tasks. Once you've added a new task, simply click on it to start and stop timing.


Requirements
============
Qt 4.7


Compiling
=========
Simply run ./build.sh in the terminal.


Running
=======
Run ./run.sh in the terminal.



Made by Shafqat Bhuiyan
